continuation of the kingship is not smooth sailing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Countless difficulties are coming one after another.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You need to carefully balance all aspects of the kingdom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Treasury, army, people, resources, diplomacy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-<strong>Make a choice-</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every decision you make will affect the future of your kingdom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you a wise ruler who loves his people like his own children, or one who will do anything to achieve his goals?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you like it or not, you need to make changes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-<strong>Multiple endings</strong>-</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each kingdom has its own story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will the kingdom fall? Or rise? Or disappear?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's all up to you to decide!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>If you are interested in this game, you may click Add to Wishlist! It will be convenient to receive game releases, discounts, and the latest news at the first time!</strong></p>",
